headline: Truist adds New Jersey team as part of targeted growth push
summary: The regional bank, which hired a commercial banking team away from Citizens Financial Group, has identified growth opportunities not only in the Garden State, but also in Pennsylvania and Texas.

headline: Truist strengthens middle market banking team in New Jersey
summary: Truist announced today the hiring of veteran commercial banking executive Gino Di Saverio, who leads a growing middle market banking team in New Jersey that includes three other recent hires.
